   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Volume 24 of The Collected Works is comprised of messages given by Watchman Nee in 1935.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>With the exception of chapter four, the messages were delivered in Shanghai during September and October of that year.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Chapter four was delivered in Chuenchow, Fukien province, in November of the same year.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>We have included it in this volume because its subject and emphasis are consistent with the content of the Shanghai messages.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>These messages reveal the excellent Christ who is in us as our victory.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Their content is rich and precious.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>May the God who commands light to shine out of darkness shine in our hearts through these words and lead us into the experience of the riches of life!</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>Amen!</S>
   </TEXT>
  </BODY>
